## |  $$$$$$\\$$\  /  $$| $$$$$$$\| $$$$$$$$| $$$$$$$\|  $$$$$$\| $$\ | $$|  $$$$$$\| $$ /  $$| $$$$$$$$  ##
## | $$   \$$ \$$\/  $$ | $$__/ $$| $$__    | $$__| $$| $$___\$$| $$$\| $$| $$__| $$| $$/  $$ | $$__      ##
## | $$        \$$  $$  | $$    $$| $$  \   | $$    $$ \$$    \ | $$$$\ $$| $$    $$| $$  $$  | $$  \     ##
## | $$   __    \$$$$   | $$$$$$$\| $$$$$   | $$$$$$$\ _\$$$$$$\| $$\$$ $$| $$$$$$$$| $$$$$\  | $$$$$     ##
## | $$__/  \   | $$    | $$__/ $$| $$_____ | $$  | $$|  \__| $$| $$ \$$$$| $$  | $$| $$ \$$\ | $$_____   ##
##  \$$    $$   | $$    | $$    $$| $$     \| $$  | $$ \$$    $$| $$  \$$$| $$  | $$| $$  \$$\| $$     \  ##
##   \$$$$$$     \$$     \$$$$$$$  \$$$$$$$$ \$$   \$$  \$$$$$$  \$$   \$$ \$$   \$$ \$$   \$$ \$$$$$$$$  ##
##                                                                                                        ##
## Flightmode Script                                                                                      ##
